00:21:16,108 --> 00:21:17,276
Educated,

362
00:21:17,526 --> 00:21:18,485
To Be a Machine,

363
00:21:19,194 --> 00:21:20,445
The Perfect Weapon...

364
00:21:21,154 --> 00:21:22,030
Elastic.

